                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18030525-37-defend286 t18030525-37-punish206"></join>
               Confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron Graham.</p>
